Package: cppinfo
Title: Extract type information from C++ sources
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: "Rich FitzJohn <rich.fitzjohn@gmail.com> [aut, cre]"
Description: Extract type information from C++ using doxygen.
    Eventually this might allow different backends such as gccxml and
    libclang.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.1)
License: BSD_2_clause + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
Imports:
    R6 (>= 1.0.1.9001),
    XML
SystemRequirements: doxygen, gccxml, libclang, Python libclang
  bindings (>= 3.4svn)
Suggests:
    rPython,
    testthat
